\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces Multi-agent audit architecture. Candidate questions are fanned out to four teams; each team independently emits per-question verdicts. Critical \textsc  {fail} signals route the question to the drop pool; C4 difficulty disagreements route to relabel; otherwise the question is kept in \texttt  {release\_v1.2}. Every agent is calibrated against the human gold sheet via Cohen's $\kappa $.}}{18}{figure.8}\protected@file@percent }
